---
title: Seared Chicken & Cheesy Potatoes with Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Infuse yoghurt with an aromatic garlic oil, then use parsley as a garnish for the perfect toppings on tender seared chicken. With a hearty side of cheesy potatoes and sweet roasted veggies, this classic meal is simple yet stunning.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
